		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've added support for MMC5 audio (pulse channels only). Another new feature is the ability to toggle between output of just the 2A03 channels, and just the expansion audio channels.<br /><br />Download <a href="http://jiggawatt.org/badc0de/mic-gwmp-6.zip" class="postlink">the archive containing the Gamecube DOL and the Wii HBC app</a>.<br />Watch <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IdZ_Q6FCnEY" class="postlink">a capture on youtube here</a>.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Unfortunately I'm foolish enough to be using 480i on a CRT, so the single scanline high white lines flicker obnoxiously.</div><br />I don't have any CRT TVs to test on. I'm using the 4:3 mode on an LCD TV.

		

		</td>
